def create_random_dimensions():
    dimension_sets = []
    
    #2 dimensions - 5850 - 11700 dimensions
    
    temp = []
    
    X = [np.random.normal(-2000, 300, 750),
    np.random.normal(-1200, 300, 1250),
    np.random.normal(-200, 400, 750),
    np.random.normal(500 , 350 , 1250),
    np.random.normal(2010 , 300 , 1250),
    np.random.normal(-800 , 150 , 300),
    np.random.normal(-2000 , 300 , 300)]
    X = [item for sublist in X for item in sublist]

    Y = [np.random.normal(150, 120, 1250),
    np.random.normal(-200, 75, 750),
    np.random.normal(500, 150, 1250),
    np.random.normal(-700, 300 , 750),
    np.random.normal(50 , 150 , 1250),
    np.random.normal(-850 , 200 , 300),
    np.random.normal(-1200 , 550 , 300)]
    Y = [item for sublist in Y for item in sublist]

    for i in range(len(X)):
        temp.append([X[i],Y[i]])
    
    random.shuffle(temp)
    dimension_sets.append(temp)
    
    #3 dimensions A - 1000 points - 3000 dimensions
    
    temp = []
    
    X = [np.random.normal(10, 3, 250),
    np.random.normal(50, 6, 250),
    np.random.normal(-15, 1, 250),
    np.random.normal(20 ,5 , 250)]
    X = np.array(X).flatten()

    Y = [np.random.normal(14, 2, 250),
    np.random.normal(24, 6, 250),
    np.random.normal(31, 5, 250),
    np.random.normal(18, 3 , 250)]
    Y = np.array(Y).flatten()

    Z = [np.random.normal(-2, 12, 500),
    np.random.normal(16, 10, 500)]
    Z = np.array(Z).flatten()

    for i in range(len(X)):
        temp.append([X[i],Y[i],Z[i]])

    random.shuffle(temp)
    dimension_sets.append(temp)
    
    #3 dimensions B - 3000 points - 9000 dimensions
    
    temp = []
    
    X = [np.random.normal(150, 20, 800),
    np.random.normal(415, 60, 700),
    np.random.normal(260, 50, 800),
    np.random.normal(-110 , 15 , 700)]
    X = [item for sublist in X for item in sublist]

    Y = [np.random.normal(54, 8, 775),
    np.random.normal(93, 25, 725),
    np.random.normal(-30, 55, 775),
    np.random.normal(21, 20 , 725)]
    Y = [item for sublist in Y for item in sublist]

    Z = [np.random.normal(-40, 25, 750),
    np.random.normal(16, 25, 1500),
    np.random.normal(90, 45, 750)]
    Z = [item for sublist in Z for item in sublist]

    for i in range(len(X)):
        temp.append([X[i],Y[i],Z[i]])
        
    random.shuffle(temp)
    dimension_sets.append(temp)
    
    #5 dimensions - 2000 points - 10000 dimensions
    
    temp = []
    
    
    X = [np.random.normal(70, 20, 400),
    np.random.normal(22, 60, 600),
    np.random.normal(260, 50, 200),
    np.random.normal(-110 , 15 , 800)]
    X = [item for sublist in X for item in sublist]

    Y = [np.random.normal(54, 8, 150),
    np.random.normal(-3, 25, 1050),
    np.random.normal(-120, 50, 300),
    np.random.normal(75, 15 , 500)]
    Y = [item for sublist in Y for item in sublist]

    Z = [np.random.normal(-40, 25, 350),
    np.random.normal(16, 25, 1100),
    np.random.normal(90, 45, 550)]
    Z = [item for sublist in Z for item in sublist]

    W = [np.random.normal(-150, 25, 950),
    np.random.normal(-50, 35, 600),
    np.random.normal(10, 30, 450)]
    W = [item for sublist in W for item in sublist]

    V = [np.random.normal(22, 30, 1250),
    np.random.normal(-45, 20, 750)]
    V = [item for sublist in V for item in sublist]

    for i in range(len(X)):
        temp.append([X[i],Y[i],Z[i],W[i],V[i]])
        
    random.shuffle(temp)
    dimension_sets.append(temp)
    
    return dimension_sets

dimension_sets = create_random_dimensions()

write_dimensions = [[item for sublist in s for item in sublist] for s in dimension_sets]

for s in range(len(write_dimensions)):
    file_names = ['2d_dimensions.txt', '3d_a_dimensions.txt', '3d_b_dimensions.txt', '5d_dimensions.txt']
    np.savetxt(file_names[s], write_dimensions[s], fmt='%.30f')

In [5]:
def k_means_l1(points, k, max_iters):
    k_centers = [list(points[i]) for i in range(k)]
    clusters = [0 for point in points]
    
    for iteration in range(max_iters):
        new_centers = [[0 for dim in points[0]] for center in k_centers]
        new_centers_counts = [0 for center in k_centers]
        for p in range(len(points)):
            min_dist = float("inf")
            center_buffer = 0

            for c in range(len(k_centers)):
                dist = np.sqrt(sum([(k_centers[c][i]-points[p][i])*(k_centers[c][i]-points[p][i]) for i in range(len(points[p]))]))
                if dist<min_dist:
                    center_buffer = c;
                    min_dist = dist

            clusters[p] = center_buffer
            new_centers_counts[center_buffer]+=1
            new_centers[center_buffer] = [new_centers[center_buffer][i]+points[p][i] for i in range(len(points[p]))]
        
        new_centers = [[dim/new_centers_counts[c] for dim in new_centers[c]] for c in range(len(new_centers))]
        
        if new_centers==k_centers:
            return clusters, k_centers
        else:
            k_centers = new_centers
            
    return clusters, k_centers
In [96]:
dimensions = dimension_sets[0]
dimensions = np.array([np.array(d) for d in dimensions])
centers = dimensions[:6]

o_t = time.time()
our_clusters, our_centers = k_means_l1(dimensions, 6, 30)
o_t = time.time()-o_t

sl_t = time.time()
cluster_preds = KMeans(6, init = centers, n_init = 1, max_iter = 30, tol=0, algorithm='full')
cluster_preds.fit(dimensions)
sl_t = time.time() - sl_t
labels = cluster_preds.labels_

print('Scikit Learn Time: ' + str(sl_t) + ' | Ours: ' + str(o_t))

Scikit Learn Time: 0.33089399337768555 | Ours: 5.079241752624512
